The '''Norwegian Federation of American Sports''' ({{lang-no|Norges Amerikanske Idretters Forbund;}} '''NAIF''') is the governing body for [[American football]], [[cheerleading]], [[Flying disc games|disc sports]], and [[lacrosse]] in [[Norway]]. It was created on January 1, 2010 by the merger of the Norwegian American Football and Cheerleading Federation (''Norges Amerikansk Fotball og Cheerleading Forbund''), the Norwegian Frisbee Federation (''Norges Frisbeeforbund''), and the Norwegian Lacrosse Federation (''Norges Lacrosse Forbund'').<ref>{{cite web|title=Årsberetning 2010|url=http://amerikanskeidretter.no/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/%C3%85rsberetning_NAIF_2010_signert.pdf|publisher=Norges Amerikanske Idretters Forbund|page=2|language=Norwegian}}</ref> NAIF is a member of the [[Norwegian Olympic and Paralympic Committee and Confederation of Sports|Norwegian Olympic Committee]],<ref>{{cite web|title=SÆRFORBUND|url=https://www.idrettsforbundet.no/sarforbund/|publisher=Norges Idrettsforbund|accessdate=15 September 2016|language=Norwegian}}</ref> the [[International Federation of American Football]],<ref>{{cite web|title=Federations: IFAF Europe Countries|url=http://ifaf.org/countries/federation/2|publisher=IFAF|accessdate=15 September 2016}}</ref> the [[International Cheer Union]],<ref>{{cite web|title=Norway|url=http://cheerunion.org/membership/nations/europe/?staff_id=92|publisher=International Cheer Union|accessdate=15 September 2016}}</ref> the [[World Flying Disc Federation]],<ref>{{cite web|title=Norway|url=http://www.wfdf.org/members-contacts/?member_id=22|publisher=World Flying Disc Federation|accessdate=15 September 2016}}</ref> and the [[Federation of International Lacrosse]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Members by Region|url=http://filacrosse.com/members-region/|publisher=Federation of International Lacrosse|accessdate=15 September 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Om forbundet|url=http://amerikanskeidretter.no/forbund/#om-forbundet|publisher=Norges Amerikanske Idretters Forbund|accessdate=15 September 2016|language=Norwegian}}</ref>
